WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:15.000
The first Ferrari model produced in 1948 was 125 F1.

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:25.000
Scuderia Ferrari has participated in in the Formula One World Championship

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:30.000
continuously since its inception in 1950.

00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:44.000
José Froilán González gave the team

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:50.000
its first F1 victory at the 1951 British Grand Prix.

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:15.000
Alberto Ascari gave Ferrari its first Drivers Championship a year later.

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:25.000
Ferrari is the oldest team in the championship,

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:38.000
and the most successful: the team holds nearly every Formula One record.

00:01:50.000 --> 00:02:00.000
Ferrari has also always participated in endurance races such as Mille Miglia.

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:15.000
Racing was considered by Enzo Ferrari the best way

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:20.000
to test new car model and new technologies.

